    "shortName": {
      "zh": "Matchking 300",
      "en": "GT HPBT"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "嵌有300格令诺玛MatchKing空尖艇尾弹头的.338 Norma magnum（8.6×63mm）弹药。这枚弹头是为冲击远距离射击纪录设计的，在远距离上表现惊人，堪称远程高精度弹药的标杆，可以胜任从超远距离射击比赛到炫耀性狩猎等的用途。特别的，这款弹药适配经典款.338 Norma黄铜药筒。",
      "en": "A .338 Norma Magnum (8.6x63mm) 300-grain Norma Golden Target HPBT precision cartridge.\nEngineered for extreme long-range accuracy, this boat-tail match projectile emphasizes ballistic coefficient, wind stability, and consistent shot-to-shot performance. It is not designed for rapid expansion, but its mass and sectional density allow it to retain energy exceptionally well downrange. Manufactured with premium Norma brass and optimized for professional marksman platforms."
    },
